{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775860419869,"sessionID":"ses_28679d8d7ffeBD6ezRS0zvKUr1","part":{"id":"prt_d79878768001DK7yLHKzOMpmHu","messageID":"msg_d798770dc001kD24iKajN051m3","sessionID":"ses_28679d8d7ffeBD6ezRS0zvKUr1","type":"tool","tool":"bash","callID":"toolu_tool-a1b88f90d5d84fb48cc3bf7bf9c27c2a","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"command":"find /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z -type d -name \"client-go\" 2>/dev/null | head -5","description":"Find client-go directories"},"output":"","metadata":{"output":"","exit":0,"description":"Find client-go directories","truncated":false},"title":"Find client-go directories","time":{"start":1775860419844,"end":1775860419867}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775860419871,"sessionID":"ses_28679d8d7ffeBD6ezRS0zvKUr1","part":{"id":"prt_d79878a81001kSrQslFnGzH5Uh","messageID":"msg_d798770dc001kD24iKajN051m3","sessionID":"ses_28679d8d7ffeBD6ezRS0zvKUr1","type":"tool","tool":"bash","callID":"toolu_tool-5c1b540c66614085a706b6d256d61491","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"command":"ls -la /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/ | grep -E \"client|vendor\"","description":"Check for client-go or vendor directory"},"output":"","metadata":{"output":"","exit":1,"description":"Check for client-go or vendor directory","truncated":false},"title":"Check for client-go or vendor directory","time":{"start":1775860419849,"end":1775860419870}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775860419884,"sessionID":"ses_28679d8d7ffeBD6ezRS0zvKUr1","part":{"id":"prt_d79878ce8001HPbbeewCdt6nhx","messageID":"msg_d798770dc001kD24iKajN051m3","sessionID":"ses_28679d8d7ffeBD6ezRS0zvKUr1","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-60d9511968a54666bf05ce1c75d85001","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/proposal.md","limit":100,"offset":100},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n100: - 磁盘空间管理\n101: \n102: ## Impact Analysis\n103: \n104: ### Components Impacted\n105: \n106: 1. **PicoD 核心服务**\n107:    - 添加新的文件操作处理器\n108:    - 扩展现有的 `/api/files` 路由\n109:    - 集成认证中间件\n110:    - 路径安全验证逻辑\n111: \n112: 2. **Router 组件**\n113:    - 更新路由规则，支持新的文件操作端点\n114:    - 传递或重写 JWT 令牌\n115:    - 处理文件操作响应\n116:    - 错误传播\n117: \n118: 3. **沙箱编排**\n119:    - 确保 PicoD 容器有足够的文件系统权限\n120:    - 配置工作空间挂载点\n121:    - 管理磁盘空间配额\n122: \n123: 4. **Helm Charts**\n124:    - 更新 PicoD 容器配置\n125:    - 配置持久卷挂载\n126:    - 设置工作空间目录权限\n127: \n128: 5. **Python SDK**\n129:    - 添加文件操作客户端方法\n130:    - 实现文件上传/下载/列表/删除\n131:    - 错误处理和重试逻辑\n132: \n133: 6. **CI/CD Pipeline**\n134:    - 添加文件操作的集成测试\n135:    - 测试文件上传/下载的性能\n136:    - 安全测试（路径逃逸、权限提升）\n137: \n138: ### Dependencies\n139: \n140: - `github.com/gin-gonic/gin` - HTTP 框架\n141: - `github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5` - JWT 实现\n142: - `k8s.io/klog/v2` - 结构化日志\n143: - 标准库：`os`, `io`, `path/filepath`, `mime`, `time`\n144: \n145: ### Data Flow\n146: \n147: ```\n148: ┌─────────────┐         JWT          ┌─────────────┐         File I/O       ┌─────────────┐\n149: │   Client    │ ───────────────────►  │   PicoD     │ ─────────────────────► │ File System │\n150: │             │                     │   Daemon    │                        │             │\n151: └─────────────┘                     └─────────────┘                        └─────────────┘\n152:       ▲                                      │\n153:       │                                      │\n154:       │                                      │\n155:       │                                      ▼\n156: ┌─────────────┐                       ┌─────────────┐\n157: │   Response  │ ◄──────────────────── │   Metadata  │\n158: │             │     (File/Dir List)   │             │\n159: └─────────────┘                       └─────────────┘\n160: ```\n161: \n162: ## Design Decisions\n163: \n164: ### 文件上传格式\n165: \n166: **决策**：支持 multipart/form-data 和 JSON Base64 两种格式\n167: \n168: **理由**：\n169: - Multipart：文件上传的标准方式，高效处理二进制文件\n170: - JSON Base64：更适合小文件和程序化上传\n171: - 为不同客户端实现提供灵活性\n172: \n173: **权衡**：\n174: - 维护两个代码路径\n175: - 稍微增加复杂度\n176: \n177: ### 默认文件权限\n178: \n179: **决策**：默认文件模式 0644，最大 0777\n180: \n181: **理由**：\n182: - 0644：所有者可读写，组和其他用户只读（安全默认值）\n183: - 0777 最大：防止意外设置可执行位或特殊权限\n184: - 防止由于过于宽松的文件权限导致的安全问题\n185: \n186: **权衡**：\n187: - 无法通过 PicoD API 创建可执行文件\n188: - 如需可执行文件，需要单独的权限管理机制\n189: \n190: ### 路径安全实现\n191: \n192: **决策**：严格的路径清理和符号链接解析\n193: \n194: **理由**：\n195: - 防止目录遍历攻击\n196: - 阻止符号链接逃逸尝试\n197: - 强制执行清晰的隔离边界\n198: - 遵循沙箱执行的安全最佳实践\n199: \n\n(Showing lines 100-199 of 1012. Use offset=200 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"- 磁盘空间管理\n\n## Impact Analysis\n\n### Components Impacted\n\n1. **PicoD 核心服务**\n   - 添加新的文件操作处理器\n   - 扩展现有的 `/api/files` 路由\n   - 集成认证中间件\n   - 路径安全验证逻辑\n\n2. **Router 组件**\n   - 更新路由规则，支持新的文件操作端点\n   - 传递或重写 JWT 令牌\n   - 处理文件操作响应\n   - 错误传播\n\n3. **沙箱编排**\n   - 确保 PicoD 容器有足够的文件系统权限","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775860419852,"end":1775860419882}}}}
