{"type":"text","timestamp":1775860437012,"sessionID":"ses_28679d8d7ffeBD6ezRS0zvKUr1","part":{"id":"prt_d7987b4ba001xQRzmRpHre6T2Y","messageID":"msg_d7987a675001V2iK4PaB5E5EWg","sessionID":"ses_28679d8d7ffeBD6ezRS0zvKUr1","type":"text","text":"Based on my verification, I can now provide a comprehensive report:\n\n## AR-016 Verification Report\n\n### ✅ PASSING Requirements\n\n**Kubernetes Client Integration (from deployment/client-go.md spec):**\n- ✅ K8sClient with dynamic client for CRD operations\n- ✅ In-cluster and kubeconfig-based authentication support\n- ✅ Informer factory setup with watch capabilities\n- ✅ CRUD operations for AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter resources\n- ✅ WorkspaceManager for lifecycle management\n- ✅ StatusReporter for periodic status updates\n- ✅ InformerManager for event handling\n- ✅ All tests passing for k8s integration components\n\n**Basic File API Handlers:**\n- ✅ POST /api/files - File upload (multipart and JSON Base64)\n- ✅ GET /api/files - Directory listing\n- ✅ GET /api/files/*path - File download\n\n**Infrastructure:**\n- ✅ JWT authentication middleware\n- ✅ Path sanitization (workspace jail)\n- ✅ Error handling with consistent JSON format\n- ✅ File mode parsing\n\n### ❌ FAILING Requirements\n\nAccording to the AR-016 delta-spec.md, the following features are **NOT implemented**:\n\n1. **DELETE /api/files/*path** - File/directory deletion handler\n   - ❌ DeleteFileHandler not found\n   - ❌ No recursive deletion support\n   - ❌ No route registered\n\n2. **PUT /api/files/*path** - Directory creation handler  \n   - ❌ CreateDirectoryHandler not found\n   - ❌ No recursive directory creation support\n   - ❌ No route registered\n\n3. **GET /api/files/*path?metadata=true** - File metadata endpoint\n   - ❌ No metadata query parameter handling\n   - ❌ No FileMetadata type\n\n4. **GET /api/files?path=...&recursive=true** - Recursive directory listing\n   - ❌ No recursive query parameter support in ListFilesHandler\n\n5. **File operation locks** - Concurrency control\n   - ❌ No FileLockManager\n   - ❌ No locks.go file\n\n6. **Test Coverage**\n   - ❌ Coverage: 35.8% (required >90%)\n\n### Summary\n\n**Status: PARTIALLY COMPLETE**\n\nThe implementation successfully integrated the Kubernetes client-go library as specified in deployment/client-go.md, but the **PicoD file management API** handlers are incomplete. Only the basic upload, list, and download operations are implemented. The following features are missing:\n\n- File/directory deletion (DELETE endpoint)\n- Directory creation (PUT endpoint)  \n- File metadata queries\n- Recursive directory listing\n- File operation locks for concurrency control\n- Adequate test coverage\n\nThe implementation focused on Kubernetes integration rather than the HTTP file management API handlers that are core to AR-016.","time":{"start":1775860437008,"end":1775860437008}}}
